And Damn Gentlemen! And Ladies. What a GREAT episode! You all did a superlative job of bringing a 'burger' episode to bear.
My favorite part was that, and this may be a bit tight......you all brought Jackson on board for an episode. You briefly mentioned that he was a 'Make a Wish' candidate, and then never, ever dwelt on that again. YOU made him your own, incorporated Jackson into the Show. By the end, I and many others were far more interested in what Jackson had to say about the burgers, than what brought him here in the first place.
Total respect and inclusion. Kudos to you for pulling that off.


Class Act Ladies and Gentlemen, Class Act! I'm subscribed and continue to recommend your channel.
Love from Santa Cruz!
